name: Tonight
detailedForecast: A chance of snow showers before 11pm. Partly cloudy, with a low around 6. Wind chill values as low as -3. Northwest wind around 10 mph, with gusts as high as 24 mph. Chance of precipitation is 50%. New snow accumulation of less than one inch possible.
